Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯馬尼亞惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸 狸~~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人沒有相遇的時空 在數個其他時空可以找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使做那樣的事 對你來說也沒有任何意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問為什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和你的時空沒有相連著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說過去是不能被改變的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去關係很好 兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在預料之上 時空不安定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺 很相似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拉庫裏瑪被香格里拉介入之前非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 和大家一起去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打電話給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:21:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是說和爸爸的約會要取消了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 只是想和你說說話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 現在還喜歡媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把它當作我們兩人之間的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...媽媽不能原諒爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫你問一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約定是兩人的秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這次的約會有什麼地方想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想乘船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又是遊覽船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是乘過了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那纜車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不要逗你爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...這個電話應該接通不了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 連著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是打給我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知哪個時空的我 聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稍微聽下我自言自語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我最喜歡的佑感到痛苦的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.57,0:22:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫助他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.91,0:24:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏日的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.29,0:24:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 最近又看到幽靈了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.27,0:24:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 鴉不是什麼幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.60,0:25:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再一次好好聽我們講話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.71,0:25:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.79,0:25:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到另一個世界嗎
